 The blues hit the blue. 

00:02:42.684 --> 00:02:44.821
 But now they will start shuffling with each other. 

00:02:44.821 --> 00:02:48.140
 And you can imagine that when this molecule here 

00:02:48.140 --> 00:02:50.080
 collide with this molecule, 

00:02:50.092 --> 00:02:52.390
 it will transfer some kinetic energy to it. 

00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:56.200
 After the collision, this can move. 

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:57.880
 After the collision - 

