 I'll do it in a new color. 

00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:19.220
 What I describe is a thermal conduction. 

00:05:19.220 --> 00:05:22.400
 Which, in a certain way, you feel many times - 

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:24.120
 transfer of heat. 

